           f"평가 완료 <b>{q['evaluated']}건</b> · 판정 {q['decisive']}건 · Paper OPEN {q['open']}건 · Shadow OPEN {shadow_open}/{V914_SHADOW_MAX}",
           f"보정 승률 <b>{q['adjusted_win_rate']:.1f}%</b> {trend} · 전체 승률 {q['raw_win_rate']:.1f}% · 평균 {q['avg']:+.2f}%",
